    <text>
        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_k0yd" xml:lang="os">
                <form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>k˳yd</orth></form>
                <form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>kud</orth></form>
                <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                        <q>как</q>
                    </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                        <q>how</q>
                    </abv:tr></sense>
                <re>
                    <form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>k˳yddær</orth></form>
                    <form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>kuddær</orth></form>
                    <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>как-то</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>somehow</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>как только</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>as soon as</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                </re>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>k˳yd ræsugd dæ, k˳y!</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>как ты прекрасна!</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>how beautiful you are!</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>83</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>k˳yddær īw nyqus dæn</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>я как-то немел</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>I was somehow numb</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>59</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Восходит к иран. %i*kuda%i (%iku%i + %ida%i); ср. <mentioned
                        xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>kuda</w>
                        <gloss><q>где</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><w>kuua</w>
                        <gloss><q>как</q></gloss></mentioned>. Связь и смысловая близость между
                    %ik˳yd%i и <ref type="xr" target="#entry_k0y"/> чувствуется в приведенной выше
                    фразе (<bibl><biblScope xml:lang="ru">%sКоста%s 83</biblScope></bibl>). — Ср. <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_k0y"/> | %iku%i.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">It traces back to Iranian %i*kuda%i (%iku%i + %ida%i); cf.
                        <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>kuda</w>
                        <gloss><q>where</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"
                            ><w>kuua</w>
                        <gloss><q>how</q></gloss></mentioned>. The relation and the semantic
                    closeness between %ik˳yd%i and <ref type="xr" target="#entry_k0y"/> is seen in
                    the above mentioned чувствуется sentence (<bibl><biblScope xml:lang="en">%sKosta%s
                            83</biblScope></bibl>). — Cf. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_k0y"/> |
                    %iku%i.</etym>
            </entry>
